@host = http://localhost:3000
@baseUrl = {{host}}/api/v1
@token = Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE

### ============================================
### FILES MODULE - File Management
### ============================================

### FILES - List Files
GET {{baseUrl}}/files?page=1&limit=20&type=document
Authorization: {{token}}

### FILES - Upload File
POST {{baseUrl}}/files
Authorization: {{token}}
Content-Type: multipart/form-data

< ./path/to/file.pdf

### FILES - Get File
GET {{baseUrl}}/files/:fileId
Authorization: {{token}}

### FILES - Get Download URL
GET {{baseUrl}}/files/:fileId/url
Authorization: {{token}}

### FILES - Download File
GET {{baseUrl}}/files/:fileId/download
Authorization: {{token}}

### FILES - Delete File
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/files/:fileId
Authorization: {{token}}

### AVATAR - Upload Avatar
POST {{baseUrl}}/files/avatar
Authorization: {{token}}
Content-Type: multipart/form-data

< ./path/to/avatar.jpg

### Notes:
### - All endpoints require authentication
### - Supported formats: PDF, DOC, XLS, JPG, PNG, GIF
### - Max file size: 10 MB
### - Replace UUIDs with actual IDs from your database
